{"tid":2290873,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"部份多接口 USB 充電器   iPhone 12 或無法正常充電","createTime":"2020-11-18T10:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T15:06:29.000Z","uid":157152,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b54dde493a92eadfc6b2212a425a134711c6bef0","tid":2290873,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8bvaJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8bvaJu.jpg&h=88f62d5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有使用多接口式 USB 充電器習慣的 iPhone 12 中國用戶，最近在微博投訴，指他們的 1A2C 多接口充電器無法正常運作。當他們為 iPhone 12 系列手機充電時，只要嘗試插入或拔除另一裝置，iPhone 12 的充電過程就會馬上中斷，用戶需要拔除 iPhone 12，重新接上才可以繼續充電。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LwE8GQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLwE8GQa.jpg&h=c6122ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有中國科技博客以多款 1A2C 多接口充電器進行測試，結果如網民所指一樣，他的分析認為與充電器的充電功率和充電參數重新分配，導致 iPhone 12 的保護機制被觸發有關。後來有配件生產商承認已經出廠的 1A2C 多接口充電器，無法在 iPhone 12 上正常運作，由於充電器無法更新韌體，所以用戶至好在每次插拔其他裝置後，手動為 iPhone 12 重新連接。<br />\n<br />\n該生產商表示得悉事件後已經將問題修正，新出廠的 1A2C 多接口充電器將不會發生同樣問題。有台灣傳媒就進行過測試，發現 1A1C 的充電器都有類似問題，但問題不會在 5A1C 充電器上出現，認為與個別充電器有關，而並非 iPhone 12 系統有 Bug 所致。<br />\n<br />\n來源：cnbeta<br />\n轉自:<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/18/1a2c-usb-charger-not-working-with-iphone-12/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F1a2c-usb-charger-not-working-with-iphone-12%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1Un12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=3071ab2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/18/1a2c-usb-charger-not-working-with-iphone-12/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟用緊anker既多口火牛都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當初充唔到電,囉去問藍精靈連藍精靈都唔知咩原因<br />\n有無師兄一樣有呢D問題?"},{"pid":"9a4341beac4139ad72175561d7008e67477e41ce","tid":2290873,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"我反而用ipad 叉電器叉12 pro , 佢當左5 w 咁叉 ， 叉到半日都未叉滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc06d105aa96081fa1451e76419bc85f3cd6261","tid":2290873,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4341beac4139ad72175561d7008e67477e41ce","tid":2290873,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"我反而用ipad 叉電器叉12 pro , 佢當左5 w 咁叉 ， 叉到半日都未叉滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"係,老實講真係唔知係12問題定人地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b92f120c4be80099f694f207018e068cc269968","tid":2290873,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T19:36:58.000Z","msg":"原廠快叉開心使用中"},{"pid":"b5eb2dc7f86a73a205966c420391ce371f3f8038","tid":2290873,"uid":152559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc06d105aa96081fa1451e76419bc85f3cd6261","tid":2290873,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4341beac4139ad72175561d7008e67477e41ce","tid":2290873,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"我反而用ipad 叉電器叉12 pro , 佢當左5 w 咁叉 ， 叉到半日都未叉滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"係,老實講真係唔知係12問題定人地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T19:40:53.000Z","msg":"用 iPad 牛唔係應該有快差咩?"},{"pid":"7a554d25ae8293f2d9415ba3be7030804ab05502","tid":2290873,"uid":152559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b92f120c4be80099f694f207018e068cc269968","tid":2290873,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T19:36:58.000Z","msg":"原廠快叉開心使用中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T19:41:18.000Z","msg":"Apple 20W 牛?"},{"pid":"6158cc7574d0b17667b87eeb53e695ae716928c4","tid":2290873,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi